---
description: Coordination Memory MCP protocol
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow the Coordination Memory protocol in `AGENTS.md` (the section between the
`coordination-memory` markers).

- `completed_gate_passed` is not accepted truth — only an integrator
  `accept_event` makes work accepted.
- Claim assignments before working; carry the current `base_revision` on
  mutating calls.
- Orient with `get_team_board` / `get_assignment_detail` before acting.
- For loop-dispatched work, read `metadata.context_refs`, obey `allowed_paths`
  and `acceptance_criteria`, use `metadata.session_bind.target_actor_id` as the
  intended worker binding before any run exists, and keep run communication
  metadata current with `record_run_binding`.
